8
00:00:38.390 --> 00:00:43.240
I'll start with the more straightforward flags and work my way up to the more complex.

9
00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:45.730
First let's tackle the Bahamas.

10
00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:50.690
I could do this by drawing three rectangles in a triangle but to make things a little simpler.

11
00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:56.010
Instead set a background color on the SPG which is the same as the blue color on the flag.

12
00:00:56.770 --> 00:01:02.730
This way I only need two shapes a rectangle and a triangle for the rectangle.

13
00:01:02.740 --> 00:01:11.580
All these are recked elements and set the following attributes x y with height and fail for the triangle.

14
