74
00:04:47.800 --> 00:04:50.590
First I'll just draw a red circle in the middle.

75
00:04:50.650 --> 00:04:55.680
Next I'll draw a blue arc to get part of the lower half of the blue area.

76
00:04:55.840 --> 00:05:01.730
I'll just guess and check until I find the right mark from the endpoint of this blue arc.

77
00:05:01.760 --> 00:05:07.880
I'll draw a second arc to the tail of the blue shape once again using guess and check until I get something

78
00:05:07.880 --> 00:05:10.630
