79
00:05:10.700 --> 00:05:16.320
I'm using lower case letters so that I don't have to calculate the absolute position of these coordinates.

80
00:05:18.150 --> 00:05:21.760
This is getting closer but now my blue area is too big.

81
00:05:22.290 --> 00:05:29.210
So I'll make one more element Redpath to cover the extra area I created with my blue pass.

82
00:05:29.210 --> 00:05:34.550
I'll start by creating an arc for the head of the red area and then create one more arc to cover up

83
00:05:34.550 --> 00:05:37.670
